{"tid":1401674,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[新戰略] 示威過後，街坊進場","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:24:44.000Z","uid":188428,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fccd4aba0985b0b8521dc63f1559180e0e6f4ad1","tid":1401674,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"今晚，睇住rthk live, 我留意到一樣嘢。<br />\n<br />\nmk示威者撤後，防暴未推進填滿空隙時，有很多非穿黑衫，冇戴口罩嘅街坊，在行人路上大屌防暴警「走啦」「屌你老母」。警方不敢推進，甚至被逼後退。街坊乘勝追擊，一度走上馬路，掩護穿梭中的零星full gear示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">對住示威者，警察肆無忌憚開戰。<br />\n對住街坊，警察手足無措。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在一位警察的眼中，就只有兩種人：<br />\n「需要對付」與「毋須對付」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">警察心諗：</span></span><br />\n穿黑衫的，自然是要全力對付的暴徒。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">可是，穿街坊裝的呢？<br />\n怎麼他們也不歡迎我們去維護法治？</span><br />\n<br />\n論地理優勢，街坊可隨時彈出彈入。<br />\n論道德高地，警察不敢對街坊施暴。<br />\n<br />\n街坊嘅定位與作用：<br />\n1. 掩護示威者換裝撤離<br />\n2. 屌到警察懷疑人生<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">示威過後，街坊進場。</span></span></strong></div><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">這就是我們的新戰略</div></em>"},{"pid":"c507778a2e5d5606dd8b131c3dcad65eb9eb95a6","tid":1401674,"uid":86756,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:02:24.000Z","msg":"無撚有錯！ 黃大仙都係！"},{"pid":"0f413b5f53e50e7db60c192964b4120e07c5e55d","tid":1401674,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"街坊係掩護, 推"},{"pid":"7baf5c3b9d581f8bd4b0f388ef45c4471b7a6687","tid":1401674,"uid":108757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"對街坊射咗三發催淚 食晒<br />\n亞皆老街"},{"pid":"2c303e90ab352650d88278201d08f9fc50796a2c","tid":1401674,"uid":34394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"不過有效期短，過多兩次班狗射埋街坊"},{"pid":"b2a48362c928378a4666c2d1014fae7d3b61a057","tid":1401674,"uid":177082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"一直著緊街坊裝係旺角啲狗面前大搖大擺行<br />\n但係個問題係 自己友認唔到你 <br />\n出到黎 大家會直覺信啲Full Gear嘅人<br />\n我地街坊裝收埋Gear嘅人講野會無說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196c402d74745c4819f004d7e9252f3054e47b7d","tid":1401674,"uid":188428,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"rthk live影住mk街坊佔盡馬路，<br />\n防暴警推都唔敢推，最後更撤退。<br />\n<br />\n另外又影到，<br />\n一個街坊阿伯頂住十個防暴，<br />\n係咁問佢哋點解唔比佢返屋企，<br />\n不斷要求警方俾佢穿越條防線。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極致撚狗，由街坊做起。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f6fbfb9d2616ef2e962f918f1d5046b735eaf8c0","tid":1401674,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"歡迎美帝在港設中程導彈 HKers welcome the US to deploy a missile in&nbsp;HK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1401115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1401115</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e2ecd8032500c70fe23349816df6c9dcc221a994","tid":1401674,"uid":296329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"推，好正，圍返佢地後面"},{"pid":"b2d244b4ac8d5b0c4a55aa592b78989108315764","tid":1401674,"uid":272354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"高質街坊"},{"pid":"e5b282729b22907d3ced84af0a6555d8b55b5cb5","tid":1401674,"uid":55982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"街坊好嘢！街坊好波！"},{"pid":"8ad35734cfe836573f9648bb8033f87aee849b6f","tid":1401674,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"换裝扮街坊<br />\n<br />\n路過唔犯法"},{"pid":"b298fb8e6681f219e944dcd70fd2bce624a0d3d0","tid":1401674,"uid":253983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"hit and run 完就街坊進場"},{"pid":"7d57cf75eb4ee2897d776b12a228d6940de73df5","tid":1401674,"uid":275723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"黃大仙街坊好嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌走班狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07acf549c562b9ce5777c51acfc892612313dee0","tid":1401674,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明顯有狗扮示威者<br />\n引你地留低</span></span>"},{"pid":"237b1596e0fd103280f089f467d939bc964263f7","tid":1401674,"uid":269963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ceb722590385f52928d313e7f1a673a1e8e0089","tid":1401674,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0c6618e6a22ef298629765fe87a37d8d9d38520","tid":1401674,"uid":226716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:13:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e7496257c0ea86d582614058ff9ed750a1776ce","tid":1401674,"uid":226716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1094d8de32993f0696bb568e6ea5883d00bd4e92","tid":1401674,"uid":188428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"「過多兩次，警察會射埋街坊，點算？」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察夠膽郁街坊，<br />\n即係倒自己米<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n當某區有示威，<br />\n啲藍絲肯定會落街食花生睇戲。<br />\n有出過現場嘅，肯定親眼目睹過唔少，<br />\n你見啲天橋咁多人影相就知。<br />\n<br />\n當警察對街坊放催淚彈，<br />\n俾啲藍絲親嘗催淚煙。<br />\n佢哋咳撚到肺炎時，<br />\n佢哋就會意識到，<br />\n警察濫權終於燒到埋自己身！<br />\n企喺行人路食花生都會瀨嘢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37d7d74c725587c61d230711c6ee9007b208a6c","tid":1401674,"uid":21447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ff9b621ab23a0bd20b8fcd97d15481ef6ce7a6e","tid":1401674,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1094d8de32993f0696bb568e6ea5883d00bd4e92","tid":1401674,"uid":188428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"「過多兩次，警察會射埋街坊，點算？」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察夠膽郁街坊，<br />\n即係倒自己米<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n當某區有示威，<br />\n啲藍絲肯定會落街食花生睇戲。<br />\n有出過現場嘅，肯定親眼目睹過唔少，<br />\n你見啲天橋咁多人影相就知。<br />\n<br />\n當警察對街坊放催淚彈，<br />\n俾啲藍絲親嘗催淚煙。<br />\n佢哋咳撚到肺炎時，<br />\n佢哋就會意識到，<br />\n警察濫權終於燒到埋自己身！<br />\n企喺行人路食花生都會瀨嘢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"郁緊"},{"pid":"ef16eccfd5e8d09e9c73ba07186a387421be8143","tid":1401674,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c303e90ab352650d88278201d08f9fc50796a2c","tid":1401674,"uid":34394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"不過有效期短，過多兩次班狗射埋街坊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"中咗"},{"pid":"cfbd7d36cc760f27549e58b71410b4fb4dd664be","tid":1401674,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef16eccfd5e8d09e9c73ba07186a387421be8143","tid":1401674,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c303e90ab352650d88278201d08f9fc50796a2c","tid":1401674,"uid":34394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"不過有效期短，過多兩次班狗射埋街坊"},"cit